      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5349 - Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub narrated from Ali ibn Ri'ab, who narrated from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) regarding a man who placed his servant on an animal, and the animal trampled a man.\nImam (as) said: \"The compensation is upon the master.\""
